high_descs: Move to the cupboard to the right of the stove.
Open the upper cupboard on the right and select a large spoon.
Turn left, go to the stove and face the stove.
Put the large spoon in to the pan.
Pick up the pan with the large spoon on it.
Turn to the right, move to the table near the stool.
Put the pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan, with a spoon, on the table.

high_descs: Move to the right and face the upper cabinet.
Open the cabinet and remove the ladle.
Move to the left to face the stove.
Place the ladle on the pan on the stove top.
Pick up the pan with the ladle on it.
Turn around and walk around the counter to the other side.
Place the pan with the ladle on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan on the counter top with the ladle in it.

high_descs: Turn to your right then turn to your left walk towards the counter beside the stove
Open the second cabinet on the upper level then pick up the ladle
Turn to your left, walk towards the stove
Put the ladle on the pan
Pick up the pan and ladle on top of the stove
Turn to your right, then head to the table on your right
Put the pan and ladle on top of the table
anns.task_desc: Put the kitchen tools on the table
